BT.managers.CD

Class Method

  • java.lang.Object
    • BT.managers.CD.Attribute
      • BT.managers.CD.MethodModel
        • BT.managers.CD.Method

  • public class Method
extends MethodModel
    Class that holds information about method. It has petrinet describing it's behavior and attributes that are shared with object. These attributes are object's private, public and protected and parent classes attributes.

    Karel Hala
